   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Click on the<uicontrol> Link</uicontrol> in the email you have received. </p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="500"
                         href="../attachments/69206021/69206092.png"/>
               </fig> You are directed to the Welcome page of RFI Survey.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>View Survey</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Enter your responses for the questions.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To upload an attachment, click <uicontrol>Upload</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Choose File</uicontrol> and select the file that you want to upload. </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Enter the <uicontrol>File Name</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Attach</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>After you have entered all the responses, click <uicontrol>Submit</uicontrol>. You will be redirected to Thank you page.</p>
            <p>
               <note type="note">
                  <p>You can respond to the RFI only once. Once you click Submit, you will not able to edit or resend the responses to RFI Survey. If you try to click the link in your email after you have responded to RFI Survey, you will be redirected to Thank you page.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
